Homo sapiens -LRB- Latin : `` wise man '' -RRB- is the binomial nomenclature -LRB- also known as the scientific name -RRB- for the only extant human species .
Homo is the human genus , which also includes Neanderthals and many other extinct species of hominin ; H. sapiens is the only surviving species of the genus Homo .
Modern humans are the subspecies Homo sapiens sapiens , which differentiates them from what has been argued to be their direct ancestor , Homo sapiens idaltu .
The ingenuity and adaptability of Homo sapiens has led to it becoming the most influential species on Earth ; it is currently deemed of least concern on the Red List of endangered species by the International Union for Conservation of Nature .